Module io.netty5.transport
Package io.netty5.channel

Interface AddressedEnvelope<M,​A extends SocketAddress>

  • Type Parameters:
    M - the type of the wrapped message
    A - the type of the address
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BufferAddressedEnvelope, BufferDatagramPacket, BufferDomainDatagramPacket, BufferSegmentedDatagramPacket, DatagramDnsQuery, DatagramDnsResponse, DatagramPacket, DefaultAddressedEnvelope, DefaultBufferAddressedEnvelope, DefaultByteBufAddressedEnvelope, DomainDatagramPacket, SegmentedDatagramPacket
    public interface AddressedEnvelope<M,​A extends SocketAddress>
    A message that wraps another message with a sender address and a recipient address.
